{"type": "article", "id": 11602, "title": "Mary Katrantzou&Adidas Originals 联名系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-03T11:30:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000050VRkyA1c2zS8xT7hN.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国时装设计师 Mary Katrantzou 一直以来以古典与现代的完美结合闻名，近日，她和 Adidas Originals 联手推出了一个合作系列，在这个系列中，Mary Katrantzou 为衣服加入了独具个性的数码印花图案，在保留古典时装原型的基础上，在配色和印花上大下功夫，既复古又时尚。单品有运动外套，连身裙，夹克等，目前已经登陆线上商店，<a href=\"http://www.adidas.com/cn/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135731TYLX2fpO1IJ4DH0j.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"564\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.52222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135732f5DqxUig1AHb8Q3e.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"767\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135732lUi1eGd0fOQxVFhH.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"788\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135733hTKD67BLNR9MZYjb.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"721\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135733teu9EWwrm5M1aTgQ.jpg\" width=\"728\" height=\"816\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.12087912\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}